data.description: Back on the market! Buyer's finance fell through.  Welcome to this glamorous entertainers delight built by First Texas Homes.  This home features a 5 bedrooms, 3 baths and a master bedroom located downstairs with huge walk in closet.  Floorplan opens up the galley kitchen to dining area and living room.  Large media room provides a comfortable space for watching sports and movies and features a built in cabinet bar area.  The neighborhood has a great community pool and playground.  What a fantastic location with shops, restaurants and entertainment nearby.  Home is 2-3 minutes from the Chisholm Trail Pkwy and 15 min to downtown.
